,"turnChangeInTime":1},{"bgm":"bgm03_story23","nameNarration":"","narration":"从很久以前开始@长年持续的东西问题","narrationCoverOpacity":110,"narrationEffect":"in","narrationHAlignment":"left","narrationPosX":100,"turnChangeOut":"fadeOut","turnChangeOutTime":1},{"narration":"东边是危险的地区，聚集了很多粗暴的人@西边则冷落并试图赶走东边的人@在无数个世代之中，@我们一直耳闻目睹着彼此的缺点"},{"narration":"当然了，因为生活和文化不同@也是有可能发生摩擦的@但是，我们真的不能友好相处吗…？"},{"narration":"与过去不同，在SNS上的交流@和通过社团活动进行的交流都在不断增加@对于至今为止耳闻目睹的常识@有没有人感受到过违和呢？"},{"narration":"说过话之后发现其实很普通@在休息日见过面之后，对东西的关系感到吃惊@这样的事情，相信大家都有所经历"},{"narration":"明明如此，我们却不知为何@从上一代的人说的话@和周围的人的氛围中感到沉重的压力@不敢说出真正的想法"},{"narration":"如果有人经历过这样的事情@可以赞同一下「友好相处大作战」吗？@如果您愿意赞同@希望您可以在点击链接后跳转的网页进行署名"},{"narration":"接下来，我们将会设立@「创造神滨市未来的学生会议」"},{"narration":"这是愿意赞同的东西学生齐心协力@为了让彼此能在神滨市携手共进@而进行商讨的会议"},{"narration":"在收集到署名之后@我们将会与神滨市政府交涉@因此，请您务必协助我们"},{"autoTurnLast":0.2,"bg":"bg_adv_17093.jpg","chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":101101,"motion":1,"pos":2},{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":101001,"motion":0,"pos":0}],"deleteArmatureList":[1],"narrationEffect":"out","turnChangeIn":"fadeIn"},{"chara":[{"id":101101,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_103103/vo_full_103103-9-54"}],"nameRight":"かえで","textRight":"好厉害，@虽然很慢但真的在增加呢","turnChangeOut":"fadeOut"},{"chara":[{"id":101001,"motion":300,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_103103/vo_full_103103-9-55"}],"nameLeft":"ももこ","textLeft":"署名的数量…@势头好猛啊…"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":100901,"motion":1,"pos":0,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_103103/vo_full_103103-9-56"}],"nameLeft":"レナ","textLeft":"话说，增加的速度@是不是变快了？"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":101101,"motion":100,"pos":2,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_103103/vo_full_103103-9-57"}],"nameRight":"かえで","textRight":"可能大家都告诉了熟人，@这件事也传开了吧"},{"chara":[{"id":100901,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_103103/vo_full_103103-9-58"}],"nameLeft":"レナ","textLeft":"明明灯花和音梦@就算想扩散魔法少女的事情也没用"},{"chara":[{"id":100901,"motion":100,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_103103/vo_full_103103-9-59"}],"nameLeft":"レナ","textLeft":"真叫人搞不懂"},{"nameCenter":"十七夜の弟の声","textCenter":"那个…","voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_103103/vo_full_103103-9-60"},{"autoTurnLast":0.2,"chara":[{"effect":"fadeout","id":100901},{"effect":"fadeout","id":101101}],"textClear":1},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":103801,"motion":0,"pos":0,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_103103/vo_full_103103-9-61"},{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":832400,"motion":0,"pos":2}],"nameLeft":"御影","textLeft":"啊，是七夜碳家的！"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":100901,"motion":200,"pos":0,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_103103/vo_full_103103-9-62"}],"nameLeft":"レナ","textLeft":"嗯，谁？弟弟？"},{"chara":[{"id":832400,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_103103/vo_full_103103-9-63"}],"nameRight":"十七夜の弟","textRight":"是的@你们应该是姐姐的朋友、吧…？"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":100901,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_103103/vo_full_103103-9-64"}],"nameLeft":"レナ","textLeft":"…朋友…？@虽然很难解释，但大概是吧…？"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp3.json","id":101101,"motion":200,"pos":2,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_103103/vo_full_103103-9-65"}],"nameRight":"かえで","textRight":"这种时候就说成是朋友吧"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":101001,"motion":200,"pos":0,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_103103/vo_full_103103-9-66"}],"nameLeft":"ももこ","textLeft":"别说什么这种时候啊…@要是被误会可就麻烦了…"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":101001,"motion":0,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_103103/vo_full_103103-9-67"}],"nameLeft":"ももこ","textLeft":"那、那个，不要在意@我们的关系确实很不错"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":832400,"motion":0,"pos":2,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_103103/vo_full_103103-9-68"}],"nameRight":"十七夜の弟","textRight":"…这次的事，@姐姐应该也参与了吧…？"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":101001,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_103103/vo_full_103103-9-69"}],"nameLeft":"ももこ","textLef